          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1688471315750-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>basmati rice</strong> and 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[320ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [500ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1688471062156-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1688471062156-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1688471062156-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1688471062156-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1688471062156-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spices are fragrant, increase the heat to high and add the <strong>chopped chicken</strong> and cook for 2 min or until coated in the spices</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>almonds</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong>,<strong> chopped creamed coconut</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 8-10 min further, stirring occasionally, or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-2-1688471233894-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-2-1688471233894-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-2-1688471233894-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-2-1688471233894-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-2-1688471233894-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>garlic & coriander naan[s]</strong> to a <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p><p>Tip: For a little extra indulgence, butter the hot naan once out of the toaster</p><p>Once the chicken is cooked through, add your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>creamy free range chicken pasanda</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1688471206184-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1688471206184-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1688471206184-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1688471206184-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1688471206184-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy free range chicken pasanda</strong> with the<strong> basmati rice </strong>and<strong> warmed naan</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted flaked almonds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
